OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FAt least 27 people have drowned after
OL,8,Fa passenger ferry capsized off the
OL,9,Fcoast of Guyana on Saturday night,
OL,10,Fwith dozens more feared missing.
OL,12,FGuyanese Prime Minister Mark Phillips
OL,13,Fsaid on Monday that at least 69 people
OL,14,Fhad been rescued, but 83 others remain
OL,15,Funaccounted for.
OL,17,FAn inaccurate passenger list and
OL,18,Falleged drug use by crew members may
OL,19,Fhave contributed to the disaster,
OL,20,Fauthorities said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
