CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784650720
OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FThe captain of the MV Barima and other
OL,8,Fcrew members have been taken into
OL,9,Fpolice custody, Public Works Minister
OL,10,FJuan Edghill said at a press
OL,11,Fconference late on Sunday.
OL,13,F"Search and rescue is still in
OL,14,Fprogress," Mr Edghill said. "So to the
OL,15,Ffamilies that are out there wondering
OL,16,Fabout their loved ones, we are doing
OL,17,Feverything that is humanly possible to
OL,18,Ffind them."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@JO]vD@]OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
