PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784650720
OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FThe passenger ferry capsized off
OL,8,FGuyana's North Atlantic coast, around
OL,9,Fseven miles from shore, while
OL,10,Ftravelling from the capital Georgetown
OL,11,Fto the village of Port Kaituma,
OL,12,Fauthorities said.
OL,14,FOfficials initially believed 133
OL,15,Fpeople were on board, but after
OL,16,Freviewing footage from the boarding
OL,17,Fprocess, they revised the figure to
OL,18,F179 passengers and crew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
