FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784650720
OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FAir traffic control received a
OL,8,Fdistress call from the ferry at around
OL,9,F11pm on Saturday, prompting a search
OL,10,Fand rescue operation.
OL,12,FMr Edghill said the initial rescue
OL,13,Feffort was hampered by darkness and a
OL,14,Flack of vessels equipped with scanners
OL,15,Fto detect survivors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
