CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784650720
OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FCompanies from Guyana's oil and gas
OL,8,Fsector have since deployed vessels
OL,9,Fwith scanning equipment, while the
OL,10,Fgovernment has sent divers into the
OL,11,Fwreck to search for bodies.
OL,12,FAuthorities have also expanded the
OL,13,Fsearch area from 400 square kilometres
OL,14,Fto 1,040 square kilometres.
OL,16,FMr Edghill initially said on Sunday
OL,17,Fafternoon that there was no evidence
OL,18,Fof "neglect" by the ferry operator.
