OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FAuthorities also discovered that some
OL,8,Fsurvivors were not listed on the
OL,9,Fferry's official passenger manifest,
OL,10,Fraising concerns about inaccurate
OL,11,Frecords and complicating the search
OL,12,Feffort by making it unclear how many
OL,13,Fpeople remain missing.
OL,15,FThe minister said the vessel had
OL,16,Fundergone maintenance in 2024 and was
OL,17,Fdue for dry docking later this year -
OL,18,Fa process where a ship is temporarily
OL,19,Fremoved from the water for inspection
OL,20,Fand repairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
