OL,3,CAt least 27 dead and 83 missing after
OL,4,Cpassenger ferry capsizes off Guyana
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FPrime Minister Phillips said the ferry
OL,8,Fhad reported carrying 268 tonnes of
OL,9,Fcargo, below its 284-tonne capacity.
OL,11,FHe added that the vessel was licensed
OL,12,Fto carry more than 300 passengers and
OL,13,Fwas equipped with 250 life jackets,
OL,14,Fsix inflatable life rafts and two
OL,15,Frigid life rafts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
